task-rest_bold.json.TaskDescription: Scan sessions started with the acquisition of the anatomical followed by the resting state scan (also followed by two task-related fMRI runs). During the resting state scan, participants were instructed to relax, fixate on a white cross (against a black background) and think of nothing in particular.
task-rest_bold.json.Instructions: Participants were asked to close their eyes and the room lights were shut off during the rest scan.
